          <targetxml>marginnote[@notetype='reference']/bodytext/p/text</targetxml> and
          <targetxml>ref:anchor</targetxml>
        <note>Create a random unique <targetxml>ref:anchor</targetxml> within marginnote if the
          source document does not contain one and <sourcexml>ID</sourcexml> of
          <sourcexml>ref:anchor</sourcexml> should be generated by given format
          "<targetxml>CountryCode_FileName_NumDigit</targetxml>" (i.e. CA_13107_001). </note>
